{"tid":955551,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打個飛機就冇咗$10000","createTime":"2018-12-25T13:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T14:58:21.000Z","uid":204943,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"49632354decebeb25b5df7f0f4e2c0510273fdd4","tid":955551,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"我青頭黎<br />\n個樣生得毒 20年黎女仔手都無拖過<br />\n所以我決定踏上叫雞這條不歸路<br />\n我知道聖誕特別貴<br />\n但係話哂第一次 <br />\n我想特別啲同係班fd面前威下<br />\n出門前仲同佢地講我今晚同靚女女朋友扑野<br />\n我上個月已經book定3個鐘同儲錢+彈藥<br />\n上到去雖然有啲貨不對版(瘦版欣宜)<br />\n但係我都起咗機(3cm&rarr;5cm)<br />\n準備用一個月貨仔射到隻臭雞一面都係 <br />\n做哂前戲 搽埋潤滑劑 一切ready好哂<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n點撚知入唔到吖!!!!!!!!!<br />\n條jerjer仔一去到個窿位就軟。。。<br />\n試咗成粒鐘都入唔到<br />\n之後我叫佢幫我打個飛機就走人了<br />\n呢30秒就洗咗我1萬<br />\n臨走佢知我青頭比咗封$100利是我<br />\n同我講Merry Christmas <br />\n所以我想問各位巴絲<br />\n荃灣夜晚呢個鐘數budget $100有乜好食?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faec33bcc007c14e39afa6d9d0a0e92f100bbd4","tid":955551,"uid":1487,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的<br />\n-1/10"},{"pid":"490b7503ae472cc9af7905dae24b4270dca8a0b3","tid":955551,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"4faec33bcc007c14e39afa6d9d0a0e92f100bbd4","tid":955551,"uid":1487,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的<br />\n-1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decc7435130